Package com.atlan.model.lineage

Class LineageRelation

java.lang.Object
com.atlan.model.lineage.LineageRelation
public class LineageRelation extends Object
Captures the relationships in lineage. The specific form of those relationships will vary depending on whether lineage was requested with hideProcess enabled or disabled.

  • Method Details

    • isFullLink

      public boolean isFullLink()
      When true, indicates that this relationship contains a full lineage link: specifically that fromEntityId and toEntityId both represent a non-Process asset, and processId gives the GUID of the process that links them.
      Returns:
      true if this is a full lineage link
